  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Design Coordinator (Civil/ Structural)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking an <strong>Design/ Coordination Engineer </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Design/ Coordination Engineer</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> Woodlands (Transport provided)</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $7,000 + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Review, coordinate, and manage design drawings with consultants to ensure full compliance with all regulatory requirements.</li><li>Analyse technical challenges, develop effective solutions, and oversee the planning, monitoring, and reporting of shop drawing production progress.</li><li>Prepare and manage technical submissions for materials, construction methodologies, and Civil & Structural (C&S) shop drawings.</li><li>Manage a team of BIM Modelers in the production of fully coordinated shop drawings and detailed construction plans.</li><li>Resolve design and construction discrepancies by closely liaising with relevant team & regulatory bodies.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least a Bachelor’s Degree in Civil, Structural Engineering, or related discipline.</li><li>Minimum of 2 years of relevant design and coordination experience with contractors.</li><li>Registered PE with PEB.</li><li>Proficiency in British & Singapore Design Standards.</li><li>Experience with BIM coordination processes and software.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
